<paragraph id="7851E4B065DEBF41F9D4EF13F48E2A61" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Although the specimen from IRSNB is quite old and collected from &quot;Nova Grenada&quot;, it is not considered to be a syntype of 
<taxonomicName id="2A01E460A959A912010303A2622B265A" authority="Kraatz, 1858" authorityName="Kraatz" authorityYear="1858" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Cyrtothorax" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Cyrtothorax erythrurus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="erythrurus">
<emphasis id="3806F6D533B246D36083A3D4DD240407" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Cyrtothorax erythrurus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
as the labels are different from that of the syntype deposited in the Kraatz collection (
<bibRefCitation id="849BD70369DBFA4666484255089E680A" DOI="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.423.7536" author="Brunke, A" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 113" refId="B2" refString="Brunke, A, Solodovnikov, A, 2014. A revision of the Neotropical species of Bolitogyrus Chevrolat, a geographically disjunct lineage of Staphylinini (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae). ZooKeys 423: 1 - 113, DOI: https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.423.7536" title="A revision of the Neotropical species of Bolitogyrus Chevrolat, a geographically disjunct lineage of Staphylinini (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae)." url="https://doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.423.7536" volume="423" year="2014">Brunke and Solodovnikov 2014</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
